"The maximum delay (in seconds) between the time when data is written to the "
"master and the time when it is written to a replica. If "
"``replication.sync_lag`` is set to ``nil`` or 365 * 100 * 86400 "
"(``TIMEOUT_INFINITY``), a replica is always considered to be \"synced\"."
msgstr ""

